data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home nestled in a secure gated community. The spacious residence boasts a well-though-out floor plan with a main-level bedroom and full bathroom for added convenience. Main level has an open floor plan with a cozy fireplace, perfect for family gatherings. The fenced backyard offers privacy and outdoor space for relaxation. Upstairs offers a charming loft area that can be versatile and a dedicated laundry room. The primary bedroom features double vanity sink and a luxurious master bathroom with a separate tub and shower. With all these amenities and more, this home offers both comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
